    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260770/extras/47167892348a9273ebf1fe7e07781ea8.avif?t=1756064898\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260770/extras_big/47167892348a9273ebf1fe7e07781ea8.avif?t=1756064898 width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A TWISTED PLACE is an unconventional and atmospheric singleplayer Horror game that alternates sideview gameplay with 1st-person moments for a scarier experience. Wander through a disturbing &amp; mysterious place while hiding from entities and find a way out. Interact with the environment to find tools, information and secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This demo takes place in the first part of Chapter 1 and provides 20-25 minutes of gameplay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260770/extras/79a7e66951ce03ed412fc561832c9597.poster.avif?t=1756064898\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260770/extras/79a7e66951ce03ed412fc561832c9597.webm?t=1756064898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260770/extras/79a7e66951ce03ed412fc561832c9597.mp4?t=1756064898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20-25 minutes of gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unconventional and eerie atmosphere</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jumpscares and creepy moments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parts of the game are in 1st-person view</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden collectibles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260770/extras/a91a21bea6a187f629938d15a96cdd30.poster.avif?t=1756064898\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260770/extras/a91a21bea6a187f629938d15a96cdd30.webm?t=1756064898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260770/extras/a91a21bea6a187f629938d15a96cdd30.mp4?t=1756064898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
